<%# app/views/pages/experience.html.erb %>
<% content_for :title, "Experiences — The Anchorpoint Retreat" %>
<% content_for :description, "Explore founder retreats, remote work escapes, and couples getaways at The Anchorpoint Retreat in Alma, Colorado." %>

<section class="section banner-home" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('experience-banner-1920-900.jpg') %>'); min-height: 50vh;">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="banner-home-container text-center">
            <h1 class="banner-home-title">Experiences</h1>
            <p class="banner-home-excerpt">Tailored Mountain Escapes for Focus, Creativity, and Adventure</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="founder" class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row flex-gap-2 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <%= image_tag "home/cooperate-retreats-600-800.jpg", alt: "Founder Retreat", class: "img-fluid" %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <span class="sub-heading">Founder Retreats &amp; Executive Resets</span>
                <h2>Think Clearly. Lead Better.</h2>
                <p>Step away from the noise and give yourself the space to think. The Anchorpoint Retreat offers a quiet alpine setting near Mosquito Pass where founders, executives, and small leadership teams can focus deeply, plan strategically, and return recharged.</p>
                <p>The dedicated loft workspace with mountain views, high-speed WiFi, and distraction-free environment make it ideal for strategy sessions, quarterly planning, or simply clearing your head.</p>
                <h3 class="heading-sm mt-3">What to Expect</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Quiet, private setting for focused work</li>
                    <li>Loft workspace with mountain views</li>
                    <li>High-speed WiFi for remote productivity</li>
                    <li>Outdoor trails and fresh air for mental reset</li>
                    <li>Modern comfort with 16-ft ceilings and natural light</li>
                    <li>About 30 minutes from Breckenridge for evening dining</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/inquiry" class="btn btn-accent mt-3">Inquire About Founder Retreats</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="remote-work" class="section banner-service wellness-section">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row flex-gap-2 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2>Remote Work &amp; Creative Escapes</h2>
                <p>Trade your home office or coffee shop for a mountain chalet with soaring ceilings, natural light, and total quiet. Stay productive with reliable high-speed WiFi and a bright loft workspace, then step outside for hiking, skiing, or simply breathing in the alpine air.</p>
                <p>Perfect for writers, creatives, developers, and anyone who works remotely and wants a change of scenery that inspires fresh thinking.</p>
                <h3 class="heading-sm mt-3">What to Expect</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Bright loft workspace with desk and views</li>
                    <li>Reliable high-speed WiFi</li>
                    <li>Distraction-free alpine setting</li>
                    <li>Hiking and skiing right outside your door</li>
                    <li>Full kitchen for self-catered meals</li>
                    <li>Evening fire and mountain tranquility</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/inquiry" class="btn btn-accent mt-3">Inquire About Remote Work Stays</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <%= image_tag "home/wellness-retreats-600-800.jpg", alt: "Remote Work Escape", class: "img-fluid" %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="couples" class="section">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row flex-gap-2 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <%= image_tag "home/private-gatherning-600-800.jpg", alt: "Couples Getaway", class: "img-fluid" %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <span class="sub-heading">Couples &amp; Small Group Getaways</span>
                <h2>Adventure Together. Unwind Together.</h2>
                <p>Whether it's a couples retreat, a close friends' adventure weekend, or a small family escape, the chalet provides the perfect mix of shared experiences and quiet connection. Explore nearby Mosquito Pass, Kite Lake, and Breckenridge by day; cook together, play games, and relax by the electric fireplace at night.</p>
                <p>With easy access to skiing, hiking, fishing, and scenic drives, it's a home base for creating mountain memories without the crowds.</p>
                <h3 class="heading-sm mt-3">What to Expect</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Private chalet for up to 4 guests</li>
                    <li>30 minutes to Breckenridge skiing and dining</li>
                    <li>Near Mosquito Pass, Kite Lake, and hiking trails</li>
                    <li>Full kitchen for shared meals</li>
                    <li>Electric fireplace for cozy evenings</li>
                    <li>Wildlife viewing and high-alpine exploring</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/inquiry" class="btn btn-accent mt-3">Inquire About Getaways</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
